On the Master channel in the Logic mixer window insert a down mixer with the setting '''5.1 > Stereo'''.

Do this by going to ('''insert''') > '''Utillity'''>'''Downmixer''' > '''5.1 to Stereo'''

[[File:Logic Pro down mixer insert.png]]


Then do a bounce to disk '''File > Bounce'''.


Keep the '''Surround Bounce''' check box option enabled (image below).


